; Regression test for bug #1393: lot date should be preserved, not replaced
; by the transaction date during finalization.
;
; The lot dates ([2020/09/15] and [2020/10/20]) intentionally differ from
; the transaction dates (2020/10/01 and 2020/11/01) so the test can detect
; if the lot date is incorrectly replaced by the transaction date.

2020/10/01 Buy
    Assets:Brokerage       10 AAPL [2020/09/15] @ $100
    Assets:Cash

2020/11/01 Buy
    Assets:Brokerage       5 AAPL [2020/10/20] @ $120
    Assets:Cash

test print
2020/10/01 Buy
    Assets:Brokerage                    10 AAPL [2020/09/15] @ $100
    Assets:Cash

2020/11/01 Buy
    Assets:Brokerage                    5 AAPL [2020/10/20] @ $120
    Assets:Cash
end test

test bal --lots Assets:Brokerage
10 AAPL {$100} [2020/09/15]
5 AAPL {$120} [2020/10/20]  Assets:Brokerage
end test
